title: Will Not Disappear
lyrics:
Headlights, no control
Caught in a coma but you would have never known
Hey now, it comes so slow
Is this the collision that we were bracing for?
What's the hurry?

The big idea?

You can close your eyes but it will not disappear



(Humming)

Could all be a coma and you would never know



Daylight slowly comes

You're just the collision that I have recover from



What's the hurry?

The big idea?

You can close your eyes but it will not disappear

What's the hurry?

The big idea?

You can close your eyes but it will not disappear
